28
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:03,940
Kau kenapa?

29
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:07,550
Kau mengakui cintamu
di tengah malam atau apa?

30
00:03:07,550 --> 00:03:09,900
Tidak, pasti tidak.

31
00:03:11,380 --> 00:03:14,390
Kau melakukannya!
Ya kan?

32
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,550
Kau sudah bangun.
Jalannya sudah bersih, ayo pergi.

33
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:22,320
